Circuit breaker day 28: with the ⛈ morning, I decided to make a pot of pork and century egg congee, topped with fried 🥚 strips and homegrown spring onions which are due for some ' harvesting'. 💯

We already made it to the halfway mark 👏
Hang on! 💪
